Info.plist additions applied by build.sh after osacompile:

  CFBundleIdentifier = com.crew.tail
  CFBundleName = CrewTail
  LSUIElement = true
  CFBundleURLTypes = [
    {
      CFBundleURLName = com.crew.tail
      CFBundleURLSchemes = [crew-tail]
    }
  ]

build.sh uses /usr/libexec/PlistBuddy instead of applying a textual patch
because osacompile's default Info.plist shape varies across macOS releases.
